WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:02.319 --> 00:00:03.446
Stiles. get out of
there right now. It's him!

2
00:00:03.470 --> 00:00:04.936
<i>He's the Alpha! Get out!</i>

3
00:00:04.988 --> 00:00:06.708
NARRATOR:
<i>Previously on</i> Teen Wolf...

4
00:00:07.241 --> 00:00:08.523
You must be Stiles.

5
00:00:09.493 --> 00:00:10.892
<i>That night in the school.</i>

6
00:00:10.961 --> 00:00:12.628
I felt utterly weak.

7
00:00:12.696 --> 00:00:14.296
I want to feel
stronger than that.

8
00:00:14.364 --> 00:00:16.931
I think I can give you
exactly what you want.

9
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:18.612
I know what you are. McCall.

10
00:00:18.636 --> 00:00:19.668
What?

11
00:00:19.753 --> 00:00:22.499
However it is you
came to be what you are.

12
00:00:22.523 --> 00:00:24.368
you're gonna get it for me. too.

13
00:00:24.392 --> 00:00:25.857
Are you breaking up with me?

14
00:00:25.926 --> 00:00:28.193
In preparation for
some big changes.

15
00:00:28.261 --> 00:00:30.490
I've decided to drop some
of the dead weight in my life.

16
00:00:30.514 --> 00:00:32.208
Every choice that I
made. everything I did.

17
00:00:32.232 --> 00:00:35.600
every single thing was to
make sure that she was safe!

18
00:00:38.105 --> 00:00:39.488
(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE)

19
00:00:39.556 --> 00:00:40.972
(ROCK MUSIC)

20
00:00:43.711 --> 00:00:47.780
ALL: (CHANTING) State.
State. State. State. State. State!

21
00:00:47.848 --> 00:00:49.648
(WHOOPING)

22
00:00:49.717 --> 00:00:50.717
Stiles.

23
00:00:53.403 --> 00:00:57.639
Stiles. Stiles! Has
anyone seen Stiles?

24
00:00:57.708 --> 00:00:59.708
Stiles! Has anyone seen Stiles?

25
00:01:03.964 --> 00:01:05.380
State. State. State.

26
00:01:05.448 --> 00:01:07.916
State. State.
State. State. State.

27
00:01:07.985 --> 00:01:10.919
State. State. State. State!

28
00:01:11.822 --> 00:01:13.188
(GIGGLES)

29
00:01:13.256 --> 00:01:17.242
You were pretty
awesome out there.

30
00:01:17.311 --> 00:01:18.793
Thanks. You. too.

31
00:01:20.881 --> 00:01:23.182
I mean. that's not what I meant.

32
00:01:23.250 --> 00:01:25.950
No. no. I. um. did some
pretty awesome cheering.

33
00:01:26.019 --> 00:01:27.051
You can thank me.

34
00:01:27.121 --> 00:01:28.936
You did?

35
00:01:29.005 --> 00:01:32.707
Totally. I went from. "Go. team. go."
to "Defense. defense." without a breath.

36
00:01:32.776 --> 00:01:34.776
I brought my A-game.

37
00:01:34.845 --> 00:01:39.047
State. State. State.
State. State. State. State...

38
00:01:39.116 --> 00:01:40.649
State. State.

39
00:01:40.717 --> 00:01:43.985
State. State. State. State...

40
00:01:45.422 --> 00:01:47.773
State. State. State. State!

41
00:01:47.842 --> 00:01:51.042
(LAUGHS MOCKINGLY)
Isn't that just heartbreaking?

42
00:01:51.111 --> 00:01:53.544
Gosh. I bet it causes a
lot of sleepless nights.

43
00:01:53.613 --> 00:01:55.413
You know what. though. McCall?

44
00:01:55.482 --> 00:01:59.618
I actually sympathize. which is why
I'm gonna make this mutually beneficial.

45
00:01:59.686 --> 00:02:01.353
You give me what I want.

46
00:02:01.422 --> 00:02:03.738
and I'll help you get her back.

47
00:02:03.807 --> 00:02:05.357
What?

48
00:02:05.426 --> 00:02:08.360
Well. three days makes it
just in time for the winter formal.

49
00:02:08.429 --> 00:02:11.930
Uh. think about you
taking her instead of me.

50
00:02:11.999 --> 00:02:14.177
And also think about all the
things you're able to do to get her

51
00:02:14.201 --> 00:02:16.668
out of some tight little
dress by the end of the night.

52
00:02:16.737 --> 00:02:18.457
See how this could
work out for everybody?

53
00:02:19.306 --> 00:02:20.639
(WHISPERS) Three days. McCall.

54
00:02:22.275 --> 00:02:23.408
Have fun.

55
00:02:26.079 --> 00:02:28.012
(BACKGROUND CHATTER)

56
00:02:28.081 --> 00:02:30.915
By the way. McCall...
Apology accepted.

57
00:02:31.835 --> 00:02:33.718
I didn't apologize.

58
00:02:33.787 --> 00:02:35.031
Every time you got the ball
tonight. you passed it to me.

59
00:02:35.055 --> 00:02:36.889
(CHUCKLES)

60
00:02:36.957 --> 00:02:38.940
Every time I passed the
ball to you. you scored.

61
00:02:40.043 --> 00:02:41.409
Apology accepted.

